::KitKat:;

She walked long, passing trees and trying to pick up on Scorponok's 
scent.  She did catch the faint smell of Scorponok.  She followed it.
The scent was getting stronger.  Then a light breeze pasted by her 
face.  She picked up another scent.  It was maxiaml. She transformed 
into wolf mode and picked up the rat.  she decided first to find 
Scorponok and giv him the rat.  Then she would find the maximal who 
was on the prowl. 

She followed her nose and came to the clearing where DarkMouse and 
Scorponok where at.
"Good, you finally caught her.  How's she doing?"
She dropped the rat in Darkmouse's lap and turned to look at 
Scorponok.  "Look, I'd love to stay and chat, but I have something I 
would like to do."

She turned and ran off into to woods.
